# WhatsApp Business Chatbot

This is an AI-powered WhatsApp Business chatbot that responds to customer queries based on a provided `.docx` file. The bot uses **spaCy** and **Sentence Transformers** for natural language understanding and is integrated with the **Meta WhatsApp Cloud API**.

